    "name": "怪奇酒馆 - 乱斗",
    "steam_appid": 3242010,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242010/extras/6bf484899d3cd5bd5a6347df2cd6be66.poster.avif?t=1772042680\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242010/extras/6bf484899d3cd5bd5a6347df2cd6be66.webm?t=1772042680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组建一支神话英雄战队，在时空扭曲的酒馆中与其他玩家一决高下！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242010/extras/762c2d60c5845f5da8c42a30a8df60ea.avif?t=1772042680\" width=278 height=102 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242010/extras/4c5ebc51c35df2fd64d7c462b3034ff4.poster.avif?t=1772042680\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242010/extras/4c5ebc51c35df2fd64d7c462b3034ff4.webm?t=1772042680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >召唤来自奥林匹斯的神明、阿斯加德的战神、东方的超凡武者与隐秘的克苏鲁眷族——每一位英雄不仅拥有华丽的手绘形象，更具备独一无二的被动技能和成长路线。自由编组你的梦幻阵容，无论是3人速攻队、5人控制流，还是极限单核输出，全由你说了算！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242010/extras/0f726dbcc048fb3fd999ed79f45c19fc.avif?t=1772042680\" width=312 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242010/extras/ed43e1210213aa3b3f992b953bc31608.poster.avif?t=1772042680\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242010/extras/ed43e1210213aa3b3f992b953bc31608.webm?t=1772042680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当前版本可收集与操控75+张卡牌，涵盖52位神话英雄与23种功能各异的属性卡。而这只是开始——埃及众神、中国山海经异兽等全新英雄已在制作中，你的牌库将持续扩充，策略维度无限拓展！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242010/extras/a5801f74321358deef5a6a9db1c84478.avif?t=1772042680\" width=319 height=108 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242010/extras/d95665fa11f7de35174f9e94d5889252.poster.avif?t=1772042680\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242010/extras/d95665fa11f7de35174f9e94d5889252.webm?t=1772042680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这不是简单的“放下去就行”——前排站位影响承受伤害，后排关系输出效率，侧翼可触发夹击，特定相邻英雄更可激活隐藏羁绊，大幅提升属性甚至获得额外技能！精准站位可扭转战局，失误一步则满盘皆输。真正的策略，从落子那一刻已经开始。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242010/extras/a0eec56b9799a49a42af60397b5ef352.avif?t=1772042680\" width=308 height=111 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242010/extras/3e89bfccd6471379b85877f2ac7cbef4.poster.avif?t=1772042680\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242010/extras/3e89bfccd6471379b85877f2ac7cbef4.webm?t=1772042680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >六大召唤师已就绪，每位都能从规则层面重塑战场！根据你的阵容风格，选择合适的召唤师，最大化发挥军团战斗力！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242010/extras/ab53a2b179c79bfa4b31c4b1122b3bf0.avif?t=1772042680\" width=263 height=114 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242010/extras/96f53661d3e0fed2f401d45d273a12a0.poster.avif?t=1772042680\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242010/extras/96f53661d3e0fed2f401d45d273a12a0.webm?t=1772042680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入全球异步对战天梯，与真实玩家的保存阵容实时对抗！无论是“嗜血流”的疯狂输出、“金币经济流”的滚雪球压制、“护盾反伤流”的极致防守，还是“英雄吞噬流”的诡异成长——所有套路都能在这里登上巅峰。每一场胜利都将提升你的段位排名，赛季更迭、奖励丰厚，向全世界证明谁才是真正的自走棋策略大师！</p>",
